  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca\u0db6\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dbb \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Five suspects for the murder of Kehelbaddara youth",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Gampaha police said that five people, including a 36-year-old woman, were arrested with a firearm in connection with the murder of a person in Kehelbaddara, Udugampola, Gampaha.",
        "This man was killed at a hair cutting place on the 6th of last day by two people who came on a motorcycle.",
        "After arresting these suspects and the female suspect, a group of officers from the Police Special Task Force Gonahena camp have taken steps to hand them over to the Gampaha headquarters police.",
        "Police say that the suspect and the suspect are residents of Nadagamuwa, Tammita, Makevita, Pethiagoda and Kotuguda and are aged between 29-35 years.",
        "The police said that they have been detained on 48-hour detention orders and have taken steps to interrogate them further."
      ],
